855,IssueCommentEvent,2016-06-16 14:30:06+00:00,32309114,mbj4668/pyang,7583329,dcpontius,,,150457385,226502483,"The YIN file generation worked fine, but the validation of the generated YIN files failed on improperly placed if-feature statements.

Our build output:
```

