3068,IssueCommentEvent,2016-05-02 02:43:57+00:00,15327092,moogar0880/PyTrakt,3399904,moogar0880,,,133912147,216095601,"So, after playing around with your develop branch for a bit I too am hitting the same issue. I was able to get it working by renaming `get` to `_get` and, after the class definition, doing 
