5034,IssueCommentEvent,2017-06-13 17:31:36+00:00,91222097,kkroening/ffmpeg-python,2035953,kkroening,,,235588180,308190788,"I've been meaning to add this. It'll most likely be a set of kwargs on the `output` function:
