6417,IssueCommentEvent,2017-07-14 13:02:07+00:00,63619003,klis87/django-cloudinary-storage,315080,yuvadm,,,242727005,315354125,"@klis87 good question, that's one way to do it. Another option is to take `settings.STATIC_ROOT` which is known to exist (it's required) and then use `../manifest/` as the path. Probably a better option would be to see how this is implemented in other package and use similar behavior.

