6970,IssueCommentEvent,2016-07-18 11:16:20+00:00,43645564,ganga-devs/ganga,1102021,rob-c,13271048,ganga-devs,165642890,233302457,"@rmatev The python code executed by the `diracAPI` has changed slightly. The expected output from the functions should always be wrapped in an `output` call as they're sent through a pipe which is parsed back within Ganga.
