8219,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-04 23:11:48+00:00,34739117,pytest-dev/pluggy,1085180,nicoddemus,8897583,pytest-dev,286135404,355426028,"Unless I'm missing something [in this comment](https://github.com/pytest-dev/pluggy/issues/114#issuecomment-355424803), nearly every pytest plugin still relies on the `pytest_` prefix naming convention for hook implementation, so I don't think we can't remove that support for pytest without breaking every plugin in existence. 😬 

