10117,IssueCommentEvent,2016-07-20 09:29:04+00:00,38581626,pybind/pybind11,17724047,peendebak,17565521,pybind,166441370,233899243,"@wjakob  In the docs I can find how to use the `py::buffer` interface to wrap my function, this is already a good first step.

