10121,IssueCommentEvent,2017-07-01 17:26:29+00:00,38581626,pybind/pybind11,4459524,jagerman,17565521,pybind,239947913,312444783,"I doubt this is something we can solve easily; multiple inheritance and `__slots__` don't mix well in Python.  For instance, without pybind involved at all:

