10885,IssueCommentEvent,2017-09-01 20:01:46+00:00,43091756,hackingmaterials/matminer,17284354,kylebystrom,14116185,hackingmaterials,254717169,326671757,"Yeah I'll look into this today and make those updates. I'll see if I can make the dataframes the exact same (i.e. the same columns). Sorry I didn't get the tests and references done when I first wrote up the datasets pacakge; I was rushing a bit too much.

