11373,IssueCommentEvent,2018-06-19 15:09:28+00:00,1360247,django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic,1393482,mumumumu,19997027,django-polymorphic,168251823,398434412,"I'm actually using the solution provided by https://github.com/django-polymorphic/django-polymorphic/issues/229#issuecomment-379084407 now. I'm on Django 2.0.6 and django-polymorphic 2.0.2.

```
def NON_POLYMORPHIC_CASCADE(collector, field, sub_objs, using):
    return models.CASCADE(collector, field, sub_objs.non_polymorphic(), using)

...

class MyModel(PolymorphicModel):
    fk_field = models.ForeignKey(on_delete=NON_POLYMORPHIC_CASCADE)
```
",{},NONE,User,False
