11969,IssueCommentEvent,2017-07-18 00:46:30+00:00,91356408,allenai/allennlp,1308313,joelgrus,5667695,allenai,242860558,315925607,"I like this approach, it's much cleaner. But I'm not a huge fan of methods that have nearly identical names but do different things, e.g.

