12021,IssueCommentEvent,2016-04-12 23:51:43+00:00,33880218,cloudpipe/cloudpickle,306380,mrocklin,10352495,cloudpipe,147901192,209154767,"This is in Python 3.  Anecdotally I find the following behavior:

