12918,IssueCommentEvent,2018-04-13 06:59:51+00:00,26542499,uploadcare/pillow-simd,424613,lopuhin,978311,uploadcare,289193152,381043025,"@homm I see, thanks for checking this. For me, the output of the reinstall command is slightly different:
