13844,IssueCommentEvent,2018-01-09 07:37:50+00:00,46374199,IntelRealSense/librealsense,17897861,ev-mp,14095512,IntelRealSense,284034885,356203649,"Hi  @SubhiH ,
AERO board comes with a dedicated APEX connector which is compatible with R200 camera only. 
The USB OTG port is a development/debugging access point.  Connecting R200/SR300 to this port for USB3 streaming requires additional steps- 
- Before powering up Aero board connect USB2 hub with KB+Mouse to OTG port.
- Power up and proceed with OS boot.
- When OS is loaded - disconnect USB2 Hub and connect a **self-powered USB3 hub**.
- Connect the camera to the powered USB3 hub 

Please follow the links in  [914](https://github.com/IntelRealSense/librealsense/issues/914) to the official AERO forum threads for more details .",{},COLLABORATOR,User,False
