14645,IssueCommentEvent,2015-04-20 14:27:34+00:00,23924195,Lasagne/Lasagne,629706,f0k,11752110,Lasagne,63232905,94467277,"> The use case for `Objective` is to avoid having to manually declare Theano variables.

