14705,IssueCommentEvent,2018-03-05 08:44:48+00:00,61572326,DataDog/dd-trace-py,1560405,palazzem,365230,DataDog,301979635,370347719,"Hello @ndkv! can you update your snippet in this way?
```python
from ddtrace import tracer
from ddtrace.contrib.requests import patch
patch()

import requests

with tracer.trace('root.span', service='request_example'):
    requests.get(""http://www.datadog.com"")
