15409,IssueCommentEvent,2017-08-19 17:31:12+00:00,43686408,OCA/pylint-odoo,16363083,mapuerta,7600578,OCA,249781007,323536802,"Hi @moylop260 @jcdrubay  

i resolved this problem, deleted file `entry_points.txt` in folder cli_helpers-0.2.3.dist-info 

Here is the Dockerfile with change mentioned

```
FROM ubuntu:16.04

RUN apt-get update && \
    apt-get install -y python-pip nodejs npm git && \
    pip install -U pip && \
    pip install -U setuptools pylint==1.6.4 pylint-plugin-utils==0.2.4 pbr==3.0.0 && \
    npm install eslint
RUN pip install cli-helpers
RUN rm -rf  /usr/local/lib/python2.7/dist-packages/cli_helpers-0.2.3.dist-info/entry_points.txt
RUN pip install --upgrade --pre pylint-odoo
RUN pip install --upgrade git+https://github.com/oca/pylint-odoo.git
```

Here [video](https://asciinema.org/a/gqEuZsUtleLuDcC5IR41YOfEo) with debugging of build of image",{},,User,False
