17464,IssueCommentEvent,2017-06-12 00:04:19+00:00,68402336,streamlink/streamlink,1396878,gravyboat,22243823,streamlink,235064771,307665829,"I agree with @bastimeyer and his response covers the concerns I have thoroughly. We generally try to keep Streamlink exceptionally light with check ins (so much so that we even dropped checking for Streamlink updates automatically!) and that's something I really like about this project. We allow for integrations and wrappers pretty easily but the core portion of Streamlink needs to try and stay tightly focused on what it was originally designed for, otherwise it will quickly become bloated.",{},,User,False
