17672,IssueCommentEvent,2016-08-15 01:54:30+00:00,26516210,certbot/certbot,91933,Daniel15,17889013,certbot,165414921,239714612,"Currently the docs at https://certbot.eff.org/#debianjessie-nginx say this:

